{
  "stem": "18626.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 394.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She opened the door and I came in very fast in that stable, where the cows-- eight or 10 cows-- were all standing right there, and hid in the hay.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I walked in in that stable, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] paradise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Heaven.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The warmth from the cows, from the hay, from that stable, from being frozen so many days, being chased through woods, cities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from that valley all night in the-- in the snow and in the cold.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When you walk in in a stable from cows-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people got to have experienced that, to be frozen and walking in the stable of cows.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's like adrenaline to your heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The warmth took me around so much that I felt I'm going to fall asleep right now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was hiding me where the cows, you know, eat the hay, you know, from the wooden, you know-- I don't know in English how to--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--how to call that, this--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trough.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The cows were eating from the troughs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said I should go under the troughs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she covered me with hay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I was covered with the hay under the troughs in the stable, really warmed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, maybe there is a God still.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what is it my brother, I was thinking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is with Abramkin?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother didn't get a chance to make it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It happened, everything, so fast, the situation that he remained still in the valley there with all the hundred thousands, maybe, prisoners.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How long did you remain--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was right there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hungry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the warmth took me around, and the girl brought out a big piece of farm bread, with a glass of hot milk.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was more in heaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
